<p>Rob and I had every intention of riding up Sunshine, but then, of a sudden, we chose Flagstaff instead.  So far this week, I'm two-for-two.</p>
<p>Today was warmer than yesterday, but it was still quite humid.  Rob and I were both put off by the brown cloud, which came into view as we rose above it.  Probably not good for our lungs!</p>